OL,6,FThe sister of Columba McVeigh, who was
OL,7,Fmurdered and secretly buried by the
OL,8,FIRA 50 years ago, has said she is
OL,9,F"heartbroken" after the latest search
OL,10,Ffor her brother's remains was
OL,11,Funsuccessful.
OL,13,FColumba McVeigh, from Donaghmore, Co
OL,14,FTyrone, was 19 when he was disappeared
OL,15,Fby the republican group in 1975.
OL,17,FA number of searches have taken place
OL,18,Fby the Independent Commission for the
OL,19,FLocation of Victims' Remains (ICLVR)
OL,20,Fat the remote Bragan Bog in Co
OL,21,FMonaghan close to the Irish border.
