OL,6,FThe ICLVR said it still believes the
OL,7,Finformation it was given that Mr
OL,8,FMcVeigh's body is there was given in
OL,9,Fgood faith.
OL,11,FDympna Kerr remembers her brother
OL,12,FColumba as a naive but fun loving
OL,13,Fteenager.
OL,15,FShe last saw him in 1975 when she left
OL,16,Fhim at a bus stop in Dungannon.
OL,18,F"If I had known that was going to be
OL,19,Fthe last time I would have seen him
OL,20,Falive it would have been different.
