OL,8,FColumba traveled to Dublin, where he
OL,9,Fwas later abducted by the IRA.JDympna
OL,10,Fbelieves someone still holds
OL,11,Finformation that is key to finding
OL,12,Fwhere Columba lies buried.
OL,14,F"Columba's missing 18,310 days.
OL,16,F"Just for God's sake, do the right
OL,17,Fthing.
OL,19,F"You know, we're coming up to
OL,20,FChristmas .. If they could just clear
OL,21,Ftheir conscience. "
