OL,6,FLead Investigator Eamonn Henry
OL,7,Fdescribed the "devastating" news for
OL,8,Fthe McVeigh family just weeks after
OL,9,Fthe 50th anniversary of his
OL,10,Fdisappearance.
OL,12,F"Everyone involved in the search
OL,13,Fincluding the ICLVR investigators, the
OL,14,Fforensic archaeologists and the
OL,15,Fcontractors who operate the machinery
OL,16,Fare bitterly disappointed and share
OL,17,Fthe frustration of the McVeigh family
OL,18,Fthat yet another search of the bog has
OL,19,Fended in this way.
