OL,6,F"Over 26 acres of Bragan Bog have now
OL,7,Fbeen searched and while we continue to
OL,8,Fbelieve that the information we are
OL,9,Fworking on has been given in good
OL,10,Ffaith clearly there is still something
OL,11,Fmissing."
OL,13,FHe added: "I can assure the McVeigh
OL,14,Ffamily and the other families of the
OL,15,FDisappeared who give them invaluable
OL,16,Fsupport that the commission remains
OL,17,Ffully committed to finding Columba and
OL,18,Fwe will not rest until his remains are
OL,19,Freturned and he receives the Christian
OL,20,Fburial that he has been denied for far
OL,21,Ftoo long."
